{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_12_level_main_12-10_beg","storyGroup":"main_12","storySort":130,"storyDependence":"main_12_level_main_12-10_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"12-12","storyName":"脱帽致敬","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_12-10_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_12-10","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":13,"next":15,"characters":["阿米娅","推进之王","卡铎尔","萨卡兹老人","？？？","考伯特","珀茜瓦尔","伊内丝","戴菲恩","“灰礼帽”"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"dialog","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":6},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_37_g1_glasgowboxinggym.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":9,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":12,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"百分之六十的感染者是在一个星期内被感染的。他们的情况都恶化得相当迅速。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"几乎每个人都有滥用源石技艺的倾向，他们还来不及学习如何成为一个感染者，如何作为一个感染者活下去。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"如果闪灵小姐在......不，哪怕是一位最普通的罗德岛医疗干员，都会比我做得好得多。","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我能做的，实在太少了。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"不用责怪自己，阿米娅，你始终在做。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"以前，诺伯特区的感染者并不多。这里的人的确都在与生活搏斗，但无论如何，这里毕竟是伦蒂尼姆。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"在离开这里很久之后，我才慢慢意识到自己的幸运。我曾以为理所当然的事物，很可能只是好运带来的例外。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"人们会因为所处的环境而错误地估计自己的能力，误以为自己的生活是自己凭努力挣来......","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"直到崩塌的时刻来临，才能认识到或许自己只是投了个好胎。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"charslot","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"哈，真是了不起的自省精神，维娜殿下。","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"所以，这才是你们回来的目的？在这里发展一大批自己的崇拜者，然后帮助你登上王位？","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"哈，我真是蠢透了，我曾经还真的以为......你是他们说的那个重情重义的“推进之王”。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0","id":39},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"这不是我的本意，卡铎尔。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我从不声称自己是什么殿下，但是在那个情况下......摩根用的这一招的确有效。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"卡铎尔，你之前总是在说“团结”，无论如何，这确实是个——","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"真是荣幸，我获得了维娜殿下的夸赞！","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_862_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"多感人啊，我们简直应该握握手，再找您的皇家摄影师给我们照一张合影？","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我不知道哪里触怒了你，卡铎尔，我认为我们应该是一边的。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......一边的？","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"瞧瞧，你们多纯洁无瑕......而我们呢？","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......前些天，我们刚把一对老夫妇赶了出去。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"他们是我租的公寓的邻居，他们以前对我还不赖，偶尔会把做了太多的炸鳞肉分给我。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"在我们刚被萨卡兹拎出家门，带到这片封锁区的时候，我看到他们在人群中慌张地四处乱跑，一次次被冲散，又努力握住彼此的手......","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我不忍心，于是就把他们带来了拳馆。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"那位老太太干活很勤快，帮了我们不少忙。至于那老头......好吧，起码他很会讲笑话，和他守夜永远不会无聊。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"但是几天前，我们让他们离开了这里。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"戴菲恩留了两天的口粮给他们，把他们安置在萨迪商场下的停车场里。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"那商场肯定已经被人搜刮了无数遍，但如果运气够好，可能也能发现些被人遗落的食物。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......那是个坚固的避难所，起码足够安全。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"是的。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"但他们是感染者。不久前才染上的。不知沾上了哪里飘出来的源石粉末，他们年纪大了，病情发展得很快。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"而我......","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我没有给他们留哪怕一份矿石病抑制剂。因为更多年轻力壮的人需要它。","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"——","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我理解你的选择。但是......","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我知道。他们很老。他们会死于萨卡兹的法术，死于建筑坍塌，甚至死于炮声引发的心脏病——但我夺走了他们最后一点希望。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......也许他们能活下来的——但我杀了他们。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"而且我不觉得我做错了。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......你知道吗？维娜，你能想到他们离开时的样子吗？","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我能想象......","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"不。你不能。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"没有哭泣，没有哀求，没有咒骂。那老头甚至最后一刻还在和我开玩笑，嘲笑商场里曾经的那家高卢餐厅的主厨。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"他们攥着那个小小的包，包里装着他们全部的希望。就这么颤颤巍巍地，互相搀扶着走了出去。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"要是运气不好，说不定路上就会被外面游荡的疯子给抢个底朝天。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"昨天，我梦到了他们。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"你对这一切没有责任，卡铎尔，你只是——","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你以为我会梦见他们惨死的状况吗？矿石病，饥饿，或是战火焚烧他们？呵。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我......我梦见战争结束，诺伯特区回到了伦蒂尼姆，我们在重建家园。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我看见秩序被重建，城墙修复完整，我们住进了亮堂的房子。然后，在欢庆的人群中，我看见......那个老头。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"他还在。他活下来了，有时活下来的则换成了他的妻子。他或者她用那双眼睛死死盯着我，就在漫天礼花的缝隙里。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我从不害怕他们死去。那意味着我做出了一个残忍的选择，逼迫他人牺牲了，或许救了另一些。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"但如果这一切结束之后，仇恨依旧流淌在和平的圣杜娜河畔呢？他永远注视着我，询问着我——","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我该怎么回答？我该怎么离开这场战争？","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我很抱——","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":131},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"不要道歉！维娜，你不够格。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你手握着神话里才有的剑，告诉我们，格拉斯哥帮的前领袖是个国王，那些年轻人曾经追捧的暴徒是骑士，是王权的拥趸与封臣——","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"——然后你说，你回来，你该帮助我们，你可以拯救我们，我们应该团结在你的身边。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"真好笑，不是吗？在每个人经历了这一切后——","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"在格拉斯哥帮从一个在街头帮人看场子的帮派变成战争下苟且偷生的小偷、强盗和杀人犯后，你们回来了。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你们变成了国王，骑士，和道德圣人。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我真应该欢迎你，“推进之王”。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"这里没有你的格拉斯哥帮。你什么都不是，你对现在的格拉斯哥帮来说，什么都不是。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"但我们必须合作！","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"只有这样我们才能阻止——","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......才能从战争里活下来。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/59/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......你很聪明。维娜，我们不想阻止什么，你没有理由让我们为你的崇高信仰牺牲。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你们，贵族们在与萨卡兹打仗，争夺着我这辈子都未曾想过的东西。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"而我们是手无寸铁的平民，只是一点点战争的涟漪就把我们推到了这里。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"是啊，为了活下去。我会先按捺下掐死你的冲动。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"你们可以留在这里，去推动你们的伟大计划，拯救这个街区或者拯救这个国家。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"或者办完你们的事，然后和你们这次静悄悄地到来一样，再次静悄悄地离开这里。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"我对这些都没意见，“殿下”，我难道有资格提出质疑吗？","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"不。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......我只是属于格拉斯哥帮，属于你们的维娜。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_862_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡铎尔","text":"......那就走着瞧吧，维娜。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_862_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":176},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_bg_37_g4_fogblockadestreet_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":180,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#8$1","focus":"m","duration":"0.5","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹老人","text":"唔......","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":184},{"type":"charslot","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","duration":"0.5","id":186},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我一开始就告诉您了，考伯特先生，只是把物资装在车上扔出去不是个好主意。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":189},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_865_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"这确实和我想的不一样，珀茜瓦尔。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"我原以为......这多少能帮上几个人。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"他们每个人可以偷偷地拿上一两件豆子罐头，大家都可以撑到下一次补给发放。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"我应该更公开的——","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"结果都一样，考伯特先生，或许还会更惨。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"就算之前大家还会对您假装客气一下，眼下的情况您也该把自己藏起来。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"您拥有了能拯救一些人性命的物资，这是好事，但您猜，在他们眼中，您更像是个圣人，还是更像是个魔鬼？","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_865_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"哈哈，更何况，我本来就是个萨卡兹。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_865_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"这些人说的是真的吗？","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"一位阿斯兰王储？大公爵们听从她的命令即将进攻这里？","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_864_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"哼，您可不是个会相信那些传说故事的街头混混，我们都知道国王是怎么死的。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_865_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"无论他们是谁，他们都帮了我们大忙，我们该......","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":209},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":212},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"和他们聊聊，对吧？","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"伊内丝小姐！我们应该用些更温和的方式......","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"？！","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你是刚才的......","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"相信我们，我们并无恶意。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":223},{"type":"charslot","id":224},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"226","text":"我们只是想与二位交流一下。"}},"values":[],"id":225},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":226,"end":242},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......你觉得我会信吗，一个用兜帽藏住脸的家伙，还有一个萨卡兹雇佣兵，声称你们和阿斯兰王是一伙的？","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"哼，这片大地上什么都可能发生。","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我自己也很意外，居然有一天会被加上个这样的身份。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......你们想干什么？","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你们是日落街酒店的人，对吧？","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"看来两位掌握了些特别的渠道。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"有一位好心的萨卡兹雇佣兵给我们送了些物资，不算多，但我想着......","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"别着急解释，老先生，我们可以慢慢聊。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":243},{"type":"charslot","id":244},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"246","text":"对于二位，我们也有些很吸引人的提案。"}},"values":[],"id":245},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":246,"end":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"好吧，只要你们真的打算帮诺伯特区的人一把，是谁都无所谓。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":251},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":252},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":253},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":254},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_bg_37_g6_hotellobby.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":255},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":257},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":258,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":259},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":260},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":262},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#5$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":264},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这家酒店居然还能进入......从外面的情况来看，我以为这里已经毁了。","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我可以向你抱怨五个小时要把外面装扮成一片废墟有多不容易。","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"我们只是不想惹上麻烦，考伯特先生不是个擅长打架的人。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"希望你们不要责怪我，我只是想......尽量维护这家酒店的体面。","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"这里曾是个了不起的地方，我在这里工作了一辈子啦，我不忍心自己曾经的心血也变成一片灰烬。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我很理解，考伯特先生，我也记得这里曾经的样子。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"炫目的水晶吊灯，热情的门童和侍应，还有那些华丽的套房。","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我还记得，挂在门口的那些漂亮饰旗。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"饰旗......看来，您也曾是我们酒店一位尊贵的客人。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......很多年前。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这些事我们可以以后再谈，听二位说，有一位萨卡兹雇佣兵在给你们提供食物？","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"是的，是一个自称明椒的姑娘，我猜，她做这些应该也很不容易。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"明椒？","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":291},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"left","id":292},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"294","text":"你知道这位叫明椒的雇佣兵吗，伊内丝？"}},"values":[],"id":293},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":294,"end":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......我看过阿斯卡纶前段时间在海布里区行动的简报，其中提到了这位雇佣兵。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":297},{"type":"charslot","id":298},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"300","text":"我想起来了，是她放走了凯瑟琳。"}},"values":[],"id":299},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":300,"end":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"曼弗雷德逮捕了她，我还以为她已经死了。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这么说，这真的是一位好心的萨卡兹？","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"不，这意味着，投放食物这件事本身很可能是在曼弗雷德的计划之内。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"军事委员会需要诺伯特区的人继续活着，起码暂时活着。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"他们在等待什么？","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们现在没时间关心萨卡兹的计划，罗德岛的两位。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我知道这家酒店拥有一座通讯站，我需要借用它。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你想干什么？","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"联络大公爵，让他们支援这里。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"所以，你们那位“殿下”的故事果然是假的。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你们给了诺伯特区的市民们一个虚假的承诺。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们正努力把它变为现实！","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"只要我们发出广播，大公爵们就不会坐视不管，我可以保证。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你这么相信那些贵族们的道德？","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我只是相信他们的野心。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"广播了之后呢？这里的频段无法加密，萨卡兹一样能收到你的广播。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"维娜小姐告诉我，她会和格拉斯哥帮的人组织一次针对封锁墙的突围行动，只要突围成功，封锁区之外就有能通向地块外的暗道。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"她们当年用过一次。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"而我们只需要坚持到大公爵发动进攻。","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"这次“坚持”，会是多久？","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"四个小时以内。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"你说得很有把握。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"离开地块之后呢？这里可是战场。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......到时候再说。我们没办法事事考虑周全。","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"只要能离开这里，之后的事情总能......","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"打断一下，这家酒店有收留别的客人吗？","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"啊？没有，当然没有......","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"这些日子，只有我和珀茜瓦尔藏在这里。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"——","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-7$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"charslot","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magic_1","volume":"0.7","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":371},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_m","volume":"0.6","id":372},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":375},{"type":"charslot","id":376},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"影子......在膨胀？","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":379},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":380},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"躲好，跟我来。","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"啊？可是——","id":384,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"伊内丝小姐，别拉着我！","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"戴菲恩·温德米尔，如果你想活命的话，跟我来！","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"欸？","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"你，你是怎么......","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_866_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":393},{"type":"charslot","id":394},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_865_1#5$1","focus":"m","duration":"0","id":395},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","duration":"0","id":396},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"398","text":"两位，你们也请离开这里。"}},"values":[],"id":397},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":398,"end":405},{"type":"charslot","id":399},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_865_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"考伯特","text":"怎么了？这是怎么了？","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_865_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"......","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珀茜瓦尔","text":"考伯特先生，照他们说的做。","id":405,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_864_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":406},{"type":"charslot","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_865_1#5$1","focus":"r,l","duration":"0","id":408},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_864_1#1$1","focus":"r,l","duration":"0","id":409},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":410},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":411},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":412},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"Dr.{@nickname}，你......","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":415},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":416},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"418","text":"交给我。"},"2":{"id":"418","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"418","text":"不用担心，我们和他仍在合作。"}},"values":[],"id":417},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":418},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"420","text":"你更应该和戴菲恩小姐好好谈一谈。"}},"values":[],"id":419},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":420},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"422","text":"这关乎罗德岛未来的立场。"}},"values":[],"id":421},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":422,"end":424},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......我明白你的意思了。","id":424,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":425},{"type":"charslot","id":426},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"l,r","duration":"0","id":427},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_866_1#5$1","focus":"l,r","duration":"0","id":428},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":429},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_m","volume":"0.6","id":430},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":431},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":432},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"434","text":"先生，要找张椅子吗？"}},"values":[],"id":433},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":434,"end":448},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":435},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"2","id":436},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"不用了，我喜欢站着。","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"罗德岛的博士，你给我惹了个大麻烦。亚历山德莉娜殿下的身份......在维多利亚很敏感，你应该很清楚这一点。","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"我以为，对于这件事，我们是有默契的。","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"不过，唉，这件事我们可以暂时先放一边......","id":444,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"能向我介绍一下刚刚离开的那位匆匆忙忙的蓝发小姐吗，罗德岛的博士？我想认识认识。","id":446,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"也许我能和她跳支舞。","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_867_1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":451},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":452},{"type":"character","id":453},{"type":"image","id":454}],"characters":["阿米娅","推进之王","卡铎尔","萨卡兹老人","？？？","考伯特","珀茜瓦尔","伊内丝","戴菲恩","“灰礼帽”"]}